Other Intangible Assets
We amortize the cost of definite-lived intangible assets over their estimated useful lives, which range up to 20 years.
Intangible assets with indefinite lives are tested in the third quarter of each fiscal year for impairment, or more often if
indicators warrant. Intangible assets other than goodwill are included in other assets on the consolidated balance
sheets.
