RICHARD V. McPHAIL, age 50, has been Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer since September 2019.
From August 2017 through August 2019, he served as Senior Vice President, Finance Control and Administration, of
the Company, and was responsible for enterprise financial reporting and operations, financial planning and analysis,
treasury, payments, tax, and international financial operations. From August 2014 to September 2017, he served as
Senior Vice President, Finance, with responsibility for U.S. Retail finance, strategic and financial planning, and
business development activity. Mr. McPhail served as Senior Vice President, Global FP&A, Strategy, and New
Business Development, from March 2013 to August 2014; Vice President, Strategic Business Development, from
